-- string can be any text that can be wrapped in a single or double quotes.
-- string can be used to store and manipulate the text
-- string is a reference type datatype.

1. length( ) => it used to find the length of the any text. it is a built in. 
2. charAt( ) => it returns the position of any text
3. indexOf( ) => it returns the value of the first occurence of the text
4. toUpperCase( ) => returns the string to toUpperCase
5. toLowerCase( ) => returns the string to toLowerCase
